gizmo385.datastructures.sll

Class SingleLinkedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gizmo385.datastructures.sll.SingleLinkedList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - The element kept within this linked list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class SingleLinkedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>
    A single linked list where each node only knows what is ahead of it. The linked list is kept in such a way that the last element in the list will always be a null node. This linked list implements Iterable through the SingleLinkedListIterator class and each element within the list must implement the Comparable interface
    Author:
    cachapline8
